Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's really not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:11.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This isn't what I meant to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:17.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought it was normal for a girlfriend to check his mail while he's away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:21.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But once I got to his apartment,\NI wanted to go inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I love, love, love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:30.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, it smells like Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:45.00,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(276,291)}My Hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:54.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aa yume no naka de aetara yueru ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:19.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ne, kanashimi dake sora kara maiochite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:27.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sonna koe ga kimi o ima demo kurushimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:31.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Soba de te o kasanetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:35.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kono omoi wa kienai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:43.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Futari me o awasetara hontou no koto yuenakutemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:47.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kimi no kotoba, dare yori mo sekai o terashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:51.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tonari de kimi wa "Sayonara wa ai shiteru" tte, sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:53.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sunao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watashi dake kodoku o utattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:57.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Egao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Arigato wa koi shiteru" tte sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:04.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ai no world's end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're not crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:25.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I heard noises next door even though my neighbor's away, so I came to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think that's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:38.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you perform that at our concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:38.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:40.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The theme is "fear."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:41.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:47.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We want to perform something fresh and striking that will shock the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:51.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but I found something that might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, no, no! I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm really not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:59.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just make about five laps around the stage in that pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can only move about five centimeters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm still just a novice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nana-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:13.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:20.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't tell Banri I snuck into his room and did the exorcist in a fit of passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:23.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I... I can't breathe... s-seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll do anything to help, other than the exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay? Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You said you'd do anything besides the exorcist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... Nana-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:16.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yo! I know you're in there, Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:23.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why do you have a knife stuck in your stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:28.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why is your white suit soaked in bright red blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tell me, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tell me, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...mister yakuza man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:45.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I ended up like this because you ran off with the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Get the hell out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll kill you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What on Earth did Nana-senpai do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where are you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:12.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kouko Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll be including this performance in the show, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The yakuza will crash the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,By the way, this guy's Tomoyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He plays bass in our band.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're saying this was all an act?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You said you'd do anything to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So I had you be my guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And you moved fine while doing your exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you try doing it onstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, come home soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:07.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:12.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You've changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You used to always keep your hair long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:17.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought it was time for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, Linda-chan's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I heard you're attending the same university.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was surprised to hear you two are hanging out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I ran into him on the day of the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're doing well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You haven't changed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Er... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Should I get some bananas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I have some in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:59.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on. That's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:04.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can call him "Bro," if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, cut it out, you gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:16.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When I saw your face, these feelings came bubbling up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:24.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Anyway, Banri, how you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:24.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just tell him you're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Y-yeah. I'm doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:33.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go to the reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:51.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a mirror Kouko gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's kind of a protective charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Actually, kind of a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Freaking out now won't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If anything happens, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:21.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You really are like a senior and junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's like I'm hearing a club party skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, right, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't use formal language today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're classmates of the same age, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:31.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:35.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If you use formal language, I'll fine you 500 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:35.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.81,Dialogue4,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(258,166)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}HIGH SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:56.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm kind of scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are you so afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not the Tada Banri everyone wants to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't have my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know who anyone is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They'll definitely wonder who the hell I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll walk you there like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, we're moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:40.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know I've told you before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:56.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you so, so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You've done so much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And not just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:06.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And... I'm sorry for causing you trouble all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:12.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I said before that I wanted to pretend the past never happened, but I regret that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:17.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know why I couldn't be happy, even though we got to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:23.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I came here today because I want to change who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You think I can change?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:33.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You are Linda, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um, it's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:50.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...an old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,An old...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm your classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is Koichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's your classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I saw you on the way to the meeting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought, "Oh! It's Tada Banri!" and couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh! Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Isn't that Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's been way too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:16.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's really Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You haven't changed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:24.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Except you're taller!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I heard you're at the same university as Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:33.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So you guys stayed friends even after graduation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well... um... that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:38.35,Dialogue3,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(453,380)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Banri
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're going...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,to play dodgeball!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,During the ball sports festival in fall of our third year,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,our class split into red and blue teams and played dodgeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I pegged you with the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:06.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but you insisted the ball hit your face and got to stay in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That allowed your team to make a comeback,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:13.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,so your red team won, and my blue team lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I definitely didn't hit you in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:24.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So today, we're going to settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:31.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:37.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:39.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That was dirty, Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought you were aiming for Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That play took brains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri, the rest is up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,G-got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wipe the floor with Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Settle this two-year-old score!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm playing for real now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:02.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,H-h-hold on, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:02.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm your senior from the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you forget you owe me for looking out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:11.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who's the one who just said she'd fine me 500 yen for using formal language?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:15.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well... we should really treasure our senior-junior relationship, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:16.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're just Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Gotcha, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Face ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, Linda...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:45.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:54.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:14:00.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is how you use the face rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.71,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(383,91)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.71,Dialogue5,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(207,92)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}There's a baby
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?! You have a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:19.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, and the father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:20.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Her husband's that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You've been dating since middle school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,When did you get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:38.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Um... This time last year, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:45.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We've been together since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:47.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Does this face ring any bells?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I really don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:53.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just getting to see you again is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:02.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, you haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:07.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your hair has changed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:10.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It wasn't like this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He changed his look after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:16.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Speaking of hair, yours was terrible at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:20.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You suddenly said you were gonna grow it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:21.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:27.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You did it because you wanted to ask a girl to borrow her hair tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? For that reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:33.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ooh, what's up? Telling stories of Banri's past?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I know one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:40.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You used up all your erasers just so you could ask a girl to borrow her eraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:46.17,Dialogue6,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(267,62)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Growl
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:46.17,Dialogue7,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(425,98)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}Growl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:46.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You went on a diet so you could ask a girl if she could tell you'd lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,H-hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:51.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're... kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Banri, they're all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah. We speak no lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And this is just the tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I-I was even more hopeless than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:11.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's been a while, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is Tada Banri here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:27.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad you could come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:30.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You always cry when you're not with everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:31.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? Cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:35.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He does, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:37.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, he cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He cries so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:40.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:46.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No, you really do cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, I want a picture with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'd like one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:56.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's go, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come on, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's your chance to get your picture taken with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:12.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was worth coming home so I could have my picture taken with girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:25.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's take one together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You know those running singlets?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The ones with our names on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:49.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Everyone wore them for my sake, using dodgeball as an excuse, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:55.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess they all tried to think of things they could do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:59.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I'm impressed you decided to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:03.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Maybe Kouko-chan's accident the other day influenced you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:10.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The good... the bad... the unexpected accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:14.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,All kinds of things happen in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There are things you can't avoid, even if you don't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:17.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:24.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I decided I don't want to be beaten by the things that happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I just want to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:32.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm living now, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm living because I want be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you thinking, "What is he saying?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm thinking, "He finally said it."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:57.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,you've seemed like a reluctant survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It made me pretty mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:02.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:07.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Then what'd you come back for, you jerk?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I felt that way sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was glad to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But I was just a nuisance to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You wanted to pretend the past didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You were cautious around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:33.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I had no idea what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:40.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,But you chose to be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your past self is part of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:44.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I am who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:55.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Actually, if I hadn't met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:57.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I might not be around right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:58.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,During the accident, just before we crashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I heard a voice telling me to "just press on."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It made me reflexively press on the brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That voice saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your message from back then reached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:15.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:21.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So there was meaning in our meeting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're a senior and junior in the same club,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:35.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,you have a girlfriend named Kouko-chan, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:42.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,In any case, there's nothing wrong with the way we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It may even be for the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:47.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah. I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Could you wait here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a picture of the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I want to show Kouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:29.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are my memories returning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:15.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Chigau yo mou, chigau tteba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:18.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aa, mada kizukanai no ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:24.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ni san jikan mo mae kara sono ude ni furetai noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:31.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:38.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sakebitai kimochi wa hora komaru hodo aru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:44.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Doushite doushite chittomo aa satotte kurenai no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:51.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ne hontou ni hontou ni watashi ni koi shiteru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:57.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Kosabayui kotoba wa iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Han eikyuuteki ni ai shite yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:04.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Gosen-nen go nado kyoumi wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:07.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Watashi endless de wa nai no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Itsuka wa shinu no yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:17.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Eien ni ai shiteru yo" nante yuwaretemo ureshikunai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:21.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Mazu wa watashi o shinu made
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:25.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ai suru koto dake o kangaete
